data-triple-N3.o: "Heidelberg is a city in south-west Germany. The fifth-largest city in the State of Baden-Wurttemberg after Stuttgart, Mannheim, Karlsruhe and Freiburg im Breisgau, Heidelberg is part of the densely populated Rhine-Neckar Metropolitan Region. In 2011, over 149,000 people lived in the city. Heidelberg lies on the River Neckar in a steep valley in the Odenwald."@en
